quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  55,67,"Nítorí náà, èwo nínú àwọn ìdẹ̀ra Olúwa ẹ̀yin ènìyàn àti àlùjànnú ni ẹ máa pè ní irọ́?"
  55,68,"Èso ìpanu, dàbínù àti èso rumọ̄n wà nínú ọgbà méjèèjì náà."
  55,69,"Nítorí náà, èwo nínú àwọn ìdẹ̀ra Olúwa ẹ̀yin ènìyàn àti àlùjànnú ni ẹ máa pè ní irọ́?"
  56,58,"Ẹ sọ fún Mi nípa àtọ̀ tí ẹ̀ ń dà jáde (sínú àpòlùkẹ́),"
  56,59,"ṣé ẹ̀yin lẹ ṣẹ̀dá rẹ̀ ni tàbí Àwa l’A ṣẹ̀dá rẹ̀?"
  56,60,"Àwa l’A yan kádàrá (ọjọ́) ikú fún gbogbo yín. Kò sì sí ẹni tó lè dá Wa lágara"
  64,10,"Àwọn tó sì ṣàì gbàgbọ́, tí wọ́n tún pe àwọn āyah Wa ní irọ́, àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni èrò inú Iná. Olùṣegbére ni wọ́n nínú rẹ̀. Ìkángun náà sì burú."
  64,11,"Àdánwò kan kò lè ṣẹlẹ̀ àyàfi pẹ̀lú ìyọ̀ǹda Allāhu. Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá gbàgbọ́ nínú Allāhu ní òdodo, Allāhu máa fi ọkàn rẹ̀ mọ̀nà.{1} Allāhu sì ni Onímọ̀ nípa gbogbo n̄ǹkan..",footnotes:1:Ìmọ̀nà ọkàn lórí àdánwò ni gbígba kádàrá, ṣíṣe sùúrù àti níní ìrètí sí ẹ̀san rere.
  64,12,"Kí ẹ tẹ̀lé ti Allāhu. Kí ẹ sì tẹ̀lé ti Òjíṣẹ́. Tí ẹ bá gbúnrí, ìkede ẹ̀sìn tó yanjú ni ojúṣe Òjíṣẹ́ Wa."
  65,7,"Kí ọlọ́rọ̀ ná nínú ọrọ̀ rẹ̀. Ẹni tí A sì díwọ̀n arísìkí rẹ̀ fún (níwọ̀nba), kí ó ná nínú ohun tí Allāhu fún un. Allāhu kò làbọ ẹ̀mí kan lọ́rùn àyàfi n̄ǹkan tí Ó fún un. Allāhu yó sì mú ìrọ̀rùn wá lẹ́yìn ìnira."
  65,8,"Mélòó mélòó nínú àwọn ìlú tí wọ́n yapa àṣẹ Olúwa Rẹ̀ àti àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ Rẹ̀. A sì máa ṣírò iṣẹ́ wọn ní ìṣírò líle. Àti pé A máa jẹ wọ́n níyà tó burú gan-an."
  65,9,"Nítorí náà, wọn máa tọ́ ìyà ọ̀ràn wọn wò. Ìkángun ọ̀rọ̀ wọn sì jẹ́ òfò."
  66,1,"Ìwọ Ànábì, nítorí kí ni o ṣe máa sọ n̄ǹkan tí Allāhu ṣe ní ẹ̀tọ́ fún ọ di èèwọ̀? Ìwọ ń wá ìyọ́nú àwọn ìyàwó rẹ. Allāhu sì ni Aláforíjìn, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run."
  66,2,"Dájúdájú Allāhu ti ṣe àlàyé òfin ìtánràn ìbúra yín fún yín. Allāhu ni Olùrànlọ́wọ́ yín. Òun sì ni Onímọ̀, Ọlọ́gbọ́n.{1}.",footnotes:1:Òfin ìtánràn ìbúra wà nínú sūrah al-Mọ̄’idah; 5:89.
  66,3,"Rántí nígbà tí Ànábì bá ọ̀kan nínú àwọn ìyàwó rẹ̀ s’ọ̀rọ̀ àṣírí. Nígbà tí (ẹni tó bá sọ̀rọ̀, ìyẹn Hafsọh) sì sọ̀rọ̀ náà fún (‘Ā’iṣah), Allāhu sì fi han Ànábì (pé ẹlòmíìràn ti gbọ́ sí i).{1} Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - sì sọ apá kan rẹ̀ (fún Hafsọh pé: “O ti fi ọ̀rọ̀ Mọ̄riyah tó ‘Ā’iṣah létí.”). Ó sì fi apá kan sílẹ̀ (ìyẹn, ọ̀rọ̀ nípa ipò àrólé). Àmọ́ nígbà tí (Ànábì) fi ìró náà tó o létí, Hafsọh) sọ pé: “Ta ni ó fún ọ ní ìró èyí?” (Ànábì) sọ pé: “Onímọ̀, Alámọ̀tán l’Ó fún mi ní ìró náà.”.",footnotes:1:Méjì ni ọ̀rọ̀ àṣírí náà. Ìkíní: bíbúra tí Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - fi Allāhu búra pé òun kò níí fẹ́ ẹrúbìnrin rẹ̀ kan, Mọ̄riyah Ƙibtiyyah - kí Allāhu yọ́nú sí i -, ẹni tó bí ’Ibrọ̄hīm fún Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a -. Ìkejì: sísọ tí Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - sọ pé Abu Bakr Siddīƙ ni àrólé àkọ́kọ́, ‘Umọr ọmọ Kattọ̄b sì ni àrólé kejì - kí Allāhu yọ́nú sí wọn - .